This program is used to sign and verify developer-mode files

Usage:  dev_sign_file --sign <file> [PARAMETERS]

  Required parameters:
    --keyblock <file>         Key block in .keyblock format
    --signprivate <file>      Private key to sign file data, in .vbprivk format
    --vblock <file>           Output signature in .vblock format

OR

Usage:  dev_sign_file --verify <file> [PARAMETERS]

  Required parameters:
    --vblock <file>           Signature file in .vblock format

  Optional parameters:
    --keyblock <file>         Extract .keyblock to file if verification succeeds
